name: ch150801A1
description: This dataset is about an in vitro-filled neuron morphology from layer 5 with m-type L5_TPC:B. The distribution contains the neuron morphology in ASC and in SWC file format.
mtypes__0__alt_label: Layer 5 Early Bifurcating Tufted Pyramidal Cell
mtypes__0__definition: The L5_TPC_B (thick-tufted PC_B) are similar to the L5_TPC_A but further bifurcate into smaller tufts in comparison with L5_TPC_A

name: rp110202_L5-2_idA
description: This dataset is about an in vitro-filled neuron morphology from layer 5 with m-type L5_NBC. The distribution contains the neuron morphology in ASC and in SWC file format.
mtypes__0__definition: Nested Basket Cell: These cells correspond to Arcade or Willow cells, having multipolar or bitufted dendrites without long collaterals. NBCs in supragranular layers were in general smaller in size than those in infragranular layers.
